AGGREGATION FUNCTIONS

SUM()               - Adds all numbers in a column
AVERAGE()           - Returns the average of all numbers in a column
MIN()               - Returns the smallest value of all numbers in a column
MAX()               - Returns the largest value of all numbers in a column
COUNTROWS()         - Counts rows in a table
DISTINCTCOUNT()     - Counts distinct values in a column

COUNT()             - Counts only numeric, non-blank values
COUNTA()            - Counts all non-blank values â€” text, numbers, dates, etc. 
